      "writtenOn": "2021-06-07T05:52:31Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "replaced it with filepath.Abs(\".\") due to\n\n\u003e Getwd returns a rooted path name corresponding to the current directory. If the current directory can be reached via multiple paths (due to symbolic links), Getwd may return any one of them.",
      "revId": "03481a463a47c92f4be16e16964b158bc6ea01a8",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
